{"tid":523770,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"求希臘Santorini 酒店介紹","createTime":"2018-01-09T01:50:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-12T05:34:23.000Z","uid":148290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3e6e1e0f5307556b4432f2d44c6505a175b174bb","tid":523770,"uid":148290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T01:50:58.000Z","msg":"出年6月中會去4日3夜Santorini total 4丁友，自己上網睇酒店睇到眼花，有幾間幾有興趣，但係佢地啲圖同review唔係太清晰，所以想睇下有無巴絲住過呢啲酒店，或者去過Santorini 有正酒店推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本身睇中兩日住呢間Fava Eco Redsidences嘅Altana<br />\n呢間應該confirm 會租<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fava.com.gr/#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fava.com.gr%2F%23&d=rCHP49TNAiE945zI%2FoVsGwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=218fe989\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.fava.com.gr/#</a><br />\n兩日住Kaleidoscope Cave Houses Oia<br />\n<a href=\"http://kaleidoscope-santorini.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkaleidoscope-santorini.com%2F&d=rCHP49TNAiE945zI%2FoVsGwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=bb01f76a\" target=\"_blank\">http://kaleidoscope-santorini.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n想知呢間cave house會唔會比隔離啲屋遮住一啲日落都睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同如果4人住係咪唔包上層呢個pool<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/09/094111_086167baa9d137b700b186b90d5303ae.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F09%2F094111_086167baa9d137b700b186b90d5303ae.png&h=ba15443c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n或者各有巴絲有好酒店推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBudget 120-140 euro per night per person，可以分開兩間房租，一定要有泳池，最好睇到日落(唔洗咸蛋黃)<br />\n<br />\n另外想知london直飛Santorini airport 入境大約排幾耐，想預時間book tour<br />\n同埋想知如果葡國passport 下年8月到期，會唔會唔比入境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n感謝大大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1c0de7df39b74e1a3dcfa7b3e9a7d83c9f669c7","tid":523770,"uid":148290,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T01:59:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">今年</span>6月中會去4日3夜Santorini total 4丁友，自己上網睇酒店睇到眼花，有幾間幾有興趣，但係佢地啲圖同review唔係太清晰，所以想睇下有無巴絲住過呢啲酒店，或者去過Santorini 有正酒店推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本身睇中兩日住呢間Fava Eco Redsidences嘅Altana<br />\n呢間應該confirm 會租<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fava.com.gr/#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fava.com.gr%2F%23&d=rCHP49TNAiE945zI%2FoVsGwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=218fe989\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.fava.com.gr/#</a><br />\n兩日住Kaleidoscope Cave Houses Oia<br />\n<a href=\"http://kaleidoscope-santorini.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkaleidoscope-santorini.com%2F&d=rCHP49TNAiE945zI%2FoVsGwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=bb01f76a\" target=\"_blank\">http://kaleidoscope-santorini.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n想知呢間cave house會唔會比隔離啲屋遮住一啲日落都睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同如果4人住係咪唔包上層呢個pool<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/09/094111_086167baa9d137b700b186b90d5303ae.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F09%2F094111_086167baa9d137b700b186b90d5303ae.png&h=ba15443c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n或者各有巴絲有好酒店推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBudget 120-140 euro per night per person，可以分開兩間房租，一定要有泳池，最好睇到日落(唔洗咸蛋黃)<br />\n<br />\n另外想知london直飛Santorini airport 入境大約排幾耐，想預時間book tour<br />\n同埋想知如果葡國passport <span style=\"color: red;\">今年</span>8月到期，會唔會唔比入境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n感謝大大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔記得左已經2018<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e716e39c004b7cbbf79342f920a7e2405f059b8d","tid":523770,"uid":86690,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T02:01:11.000Z","msg":"住過Adamant Suites.<br />\n對正個愛琴海加火山島, 一定睇到日落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24d027c019cd4b53bf11e39a575b13553ce87123","tid":523770,"uid":86690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T02:09:05.000Z","msg":"D相自己影, 俾你參考下.. 好靚好想再去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/09/100624_018e5653f9f7857866a79ce6a07264c5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F09%2F100624_018e5653f9f7857866a79ce6a07264c5.JPG&h=f5d3e4cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/09/100641_fecff7736c41eebce64ea594a7d2d58e.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F09%2F100641_fecff7736c41eebce64ea594a7d2d58e.JPG&h=af9c6b7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/09/100712_b9b3535c38328169dbee9485df318888.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F09%2F100712_b9b3535c38328169dbee9485df318888.JPG&h=30158994&s={SI